{
  "stem": "16503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If a person [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] couldn't-- I am not even saying couldn't walk-- if it had just tripped, they shot him right then, let them lying there, and you continued.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You didn't dare to find out if the person was dead or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Some people were thinking that they are going to escape, and I applauded them at first in my soul.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But as soon as they stepped out of the line, they were shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So that was no escape of any kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So we kept on walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We kept on walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And if you had to go to the bathroom, well, unfortunately, as primitive and as awful as it sounds, you did go into your pants, and you kept on walking.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Mother and my sister and myself-- we walked, and what we did was we put one into the middle and-- and took the one who was in the middle under the armpits.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the one in the middle, then, was sort of being dragged by the two others, and you could close your eyes and sort of doze off.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I mean, the three of us rotated, but I think I was the one who got most benefit of this protection because I just couldn't stay awake.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Then we were housed overnight in one-- in a barn, which had an awful lot of hay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we finally could lie down-- it didn't matter where and how-- and fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there was a whole group of people-- of women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I mean, now, I don't remember any men around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Maybe they were, but the SS were so predominant and so terribly, terribly cruel.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
